                <h1>Academic Council approves DKU undergraduate degree resolution</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/75e08338-aac2-4099-afd7-f3584e36550c.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Academic&#x20;Council&#x20;voted&#x20;57-18&#x20;to&#x20;endorse&#x20;the&#x20;creation&#x20;of&#x20;an&#x20;undergraduate&#x20;liberal&#x20;arts&#x20;degree&#x20;program,&#x20;a&#x20;proposal&#x20;years&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;making.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Academic Council voted 57-18 to endorse the creation of an undergraduate liberal arts degree program, a proposal years in the making.&nbsp;</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/rachel-baber">Rachel Baber</a> |
                                                                                                                                The Chronicle
                                                                            </figcaption>
                                </aside>
                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/bre-bradham">Bre Bradham</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">November 18, 2016 | 12:18am EST</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
