                                                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="mailto:?subject=Academic%20Council%20approves%20DKU%20undergraduate%20degree%20resolution%20|%20The%20Chronicle&amp;message=Check%20out%20this%20article%20from%20The%20Chronicle%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dukechronicle.com%2Farticle%2F2016%2F11%2Facademic-council-endorses-dku-undergraduate-degree-resolution" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="email" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i></a></li>
